    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于游戏</h2><strong>快播</strong>是一款关于法师战斗的策略游戏。打败各种元素的法师，成为最优秀的法师！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157320/extras/44a276a1c9a811aae3a4ee86434dde9a.poster.avif?t=1772325789\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157320/extras/44a276a1c9a811aae3a4ee86434dde9a.webm?t=1772325789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157320/extras/44a276a1c9a811aae3a4ee86434dde9a.mp4?t=1772325789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你和你的对手使用一副牌进行战斗！</h2>您和对手使用一套卡组进行战斗，这套卡组结合了您的卡组和对手的卡组--戳穿对手的弱点，丢弃对您不利的卡牌，记住对手的卡牌也能对您有利！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基于匹配规则的快节奏战斗！</h2>快播》中的战斗使用相同牌的配对规则。记住，配对越多，触发的效果就越强。此外，如果您处于劣势，而您打出的牌与新发出的牌相匹配，您就可以触发 <strong>快播</strong>。这给了你一个扭转不利局面的机会！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157320/extras/1e7182c7463e9c267bf0d8371457ee8a.poster.avif?t=1772325789\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157320/extras/1e7182c7463e9c267bf0d8371457ee8a.webm?t=1772325789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157320/extras/1e7182c7463e9c267bf0d8371457ee8a.mp4?t=1772325789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >8 个法师......以及更多！</h2>擅长不同元素的法师齐聚一堂，争夺第一名的宝座。每个法师都专注于一种元素，并根据该元素使用独特的魔法。记住，如果你打败了对方的法师，就可以把他的独特魔法变成你自己的！当你把他们全部打败后，会发生什么呢？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157320/extras/9e3c3960a46719285b4b48aec621df19.poster.avif?t=1772325789\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157320/extras/9e3c3960a46719285b4b48aec621df19.webm?t=1772325789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157320/extras/9e3c3960a46719285b4b48aec621df19.mp4?t=1772325789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自由漫游地图。</h2>游戏发生在一张按程序生成的网格地图上。探索、战斗、经商、休息，你想做什么就做什么，并从中获益！",
